## Client Environment Variables

# API Base URL (REQUIRED in production)
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.com/api

# Dev fallback: uses vite proxy /api -> localhost:5001

# Razorpay (for payments)
VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY=rzp_test_your_key_here

# Frontend URL (for backend callbacks)
VITE_FRONTEND_URL=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app

---
**Production Setup:**
1. Copy to .env
2. Dev: VITE_API_URL= (empty, uses proxy)
3. Vercel: Settings > Environment Variables > Add above
